e worldly benefit, he will never know the fragrance Paradise on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32812,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/15\/laugh-little-weep-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":13975,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: You would laugh less, cry often if you knew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cParadise and Hellfire were shown to me and I have never seen such good or evil as I have today. If you knew what I know, you would laugh little and weep often.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/10\/purpose-learning-taqwa-righteousness\/","url_meta":{"origin":13975,"position":3},"title":"Sufyan on Knowledge: Purpose of learning is to be God-fearing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cSurely, sacred knowledge is only studied to become mindful of Allah. Knowledge is only favored over other virtues because it makes one fearful of Allah.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u02bb Baya\u0304n al-\u02bbIlm li-Ibn 'Abd al-Barr 1159 \u0639\u0646 \u